<%# about.html.erb %>

<div class="about-container">
  <h1 class="about-title">About Us</h1>
  <p class="about-description">
    Welcome to <strong>Learnify</strong>! We are a platform dedicated to helping learners of all levels acquire new skills and knowledge through a wide range of courses and quizzes. Our goal is to make learning <strong>engaging, interactive, and accessible</strong> for everyone.
  </p>
  <p class="about-description">
    With a team of passionate <strong>educators and developers</strong>, we strive to create a unique and personalized learning experience for all our users. Whether you're looking to pick up a new hobby or advance your career, <strong>Learnify</strong> has something for you.
  </p>
  <h3 class="about-mission-title">Our Mission</h3>
  <p class="about-mission-description">
    Our mission is to empower individuals to reach their full potential by providing <strong>high-quality education</strong> in a convenient and user-friendly environment. We believe in the power of education to <strong>transform lives</strong> and help people achieve their goals.
  </p>
</div>

